feat(card-frame): ship `<card-frame>` molecule + showcase entry (§17.136 S0b)

S0b of the operator-locked 14-strand "unified card template" refactor.
Ships the second half of the foundation (the molecule itself); no
production callsite migrated. Strands S1-S12 swap each (kind, role)
into it; S13 cuts over the affordances + retires
`<parent-identity-strip>` + the `<children-grid>` corner-overlay
weight button.

The molecule lives at src/adapters/ui/molecules/cardFrame/CardFrame.ts
and exposes 8 named slots arranged in a 3-row CSS grid:

- Row 1 (var(--card-header-height, 22%)) -- title row with
  `icons` + `unit` + `title` + `header-actions` sub-slots,
  `subtitle` slot below.
- Row 2 (1fr, overflow:hidden) -- `body` slot consumers fill with
  kind-specific shrink-to-fit content.
- Row 3 (var(--card-footer-height, 12%)) -- `footer-left` + `footer-right`
  anchored at the edges via justify-content: space-between.

Operator pins: header height is panel-relative so the same template
reads on a focused-panel tile AND on a tiny tree-map child tile;
empty slots collapse so each kind fills only what it carries
(BSC/CBSN fill `unit`, Computed fills `icons` with sigma, AsChild
fills `footer-left` with the weight button, AsParent fills
`header-actions` with close-X + edit-pencil).

Test surface: 3 focused tests at src/test/unit/adapters/ui/molecules/
cardFrame/CardFrame.test.ts -- region rendering + named-slot roster,
slot routing, and the CSS contract (panel-relative row heights,
body overflow clipping, footer space-between).

Showcase: new Molecules-tier `mol-card-frame` section between
`mol-weight` and the close of renderMolecules(); a 14rem-tall
dashed-border demo stage mounting <card-frame> with every slot
filled by a probe span (Sigma / (USD) / title / subtitle / close-X
/ value / [weight] / age). View-source snippet added under
SECTION_SNIPPETS keyed by mol-card-frame.

sonar.projectVersion 0.2.121 -> 0.2.122. Net +283 lines (under
the 300 ceiling). Gate: PASSED (1 violation found + fixed in the
same strand -- typescript:S1444 `static readonly styles`, matches
